text: The Disputed Vote of Mr. Cayo is a 1986 Spanish movie directed by Antonio Giménez-Rico and starring Francisco Rabal, Juan Luis Galiardo, Iñaki Miramón, Lydia Bosch. ==Other websites== * Category:1986 movies Category:Spanish movies Category:Movies about elections Category:Movies set in the 1970s Category:Movies directed by Antonio Giménez-Rico
